T1  - Alterations of bacteriome, mycobiome and metabolome characteristics in PCOS patients with normal/overweight individuals.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1186/s13048-022-01051-8
A1  - Yin, Guoshu
A1  - Chen, Fu
A1  - Chen, Guishan
A1  - Yang, Xiaoping
