T1  - Fat intake pattern in women with polycystic ovary syndrome.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.rbmo.2021.08.015
A1  - Navarro-Lafuente, Fuensanta
A1  - Arense-Gonzalo, Julian J
A1  - Sanchez-Ferrer, Maria L
A1  - Prieto-Sanchez, Maria T
A1  - Cutillas-Tolin, Ana
