T1  - Profile of Daughters and Sisters of Women With Polycystic Ovary Syndrome: The Role of Proband's Glucose Tolerance.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1210/clinem/dgab812
A1  - Harnois-Leblanc, Soren
A1  - Hernandez, Maria Isabel
A1  - Codner, Ethel
A1  - Cassorla, Fernando
A1  - Oberfield, Sharon E
A1  - Leibel, Natasha I
A1  - Mathew, Revi P
A1  - Ten, Svetlana
A1  - Magoffin, Denis A
