T1  - Changes in complete blood count parameters influenced by endocrine disorders.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.5603/EP.a2021.0059
A1  - Szczepanek-Parulska, Ewelina
A1  - Adamska, Martyna
A1  - Korda, Oliwia
A1  - Kosicka, Weronika
A1  - Skowronska, Dagmara
