T1  - Effect of resveratrol on menstrual cyclicity, hyperandrogenism and metabolic profile in women with PCOS.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.clnu.2021.02.004
A1  - Mansour, Asieh
A1  - Samadi, Majid
