T1  - Prenatal androgen exposure and transgenerational susceptibility to polycystic ovary syndrome.
T3  - Comment in: Nat Rev Endocrinol. 2020 Feb;16(2):67 PMID: 31873208 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/31873208]
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1038/s41591-019-0666-1
A1  - Risal, Sanjiv
