T1  - An International Consortium Update: Pathophysiology, Diagnosis, and Treatment of Polycystic Ovarian Syndrome in Adolescence.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1159/000479371
A1  - Ibanez, Lourdes
A1  - Oberfield, Sharon E
A1  - Witchel, Selma
A1  - Auchus, Richard J
A1  - Chang, R Jeffrey
A1  - Codner, Ethel
A1  - Dabadghao, Preeti
A1  - Darendeliler, Feyza
A1  - Elbarbary, Nancy Samir
A1  - Gambineri, Alessandra
A1  - Garcia Rudaz, Cecilia
A1  - Hoeger, Kathleen M
A1  - Lopez-Bermejo, Abel
A1  - Ong, Ken
A1  - Pena, Alexia S
A1  - Reinehr, Thomas
A1  - Santoro, Nicola
