T1  - Value of selective venous catheterization in the diagnosis of hyperandrogenism.
T3  - Erratum in: Fertil Steril. 2017 Dec 12;: PMID: 29246559 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/29246559]
