T1  - Steroid hormone profiling in obese and nonobese women with polycystic ovary syndrome.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1038/s41598-017-14534-2
A1  - Deng, Yuying
A1  - Zhang, Yifei
A1  - Li, Shengxian
A1  - Zhou, Wenzhong
A1  - Ye, Lei
A1  - Wang, Lihua
